headline: Jack Henry Now Accepting Entries for the 2025 Cobalt Awards
summary: Jack Henry™ (Nasdaq: JKHY) is accepting entries for the 2025 Cobalt Awards through May 12, continuing to celebrate innovation by financial institutions and fintechs, dedication to people and communities, and a passion for reducing barriers to financial health.
